{{h1}}Feature Flags

Available commands:
- `{{@}}guide :flags/feature/list` - List feature flags
- `{{@}}guide :flags/feature/get <flag-name>` - Get flag value
- `{{@}}guide :flags/feature/set <flag-name>` - Set flag value
- `{{@}}guide :flags/feature/remove <flag-name>` - Remove flag
